<h2 class="mb-4">Privacy Policy</h2>

<p>Last updated: August 5, 2025</p>

<p>At <strong>Marutham Isai Palli</strong>, we value your privacy and are committed to protecting any personal information you share with us.</p>

<h4>1. Information We Collect</h4>
<ul>
    <li>Student details such as name, contact number, and enrolled subjects.</li>
    <li>Faculty and admin user information including mobile number, role, and access permissions.</li>
    <li>Fee payment records and communication logs (WhatsApp messages only, not the content).</li>
</ul>

<h4>2. How We Use the Information</h4>
<ul>
    <li>To manage student enrollment, batches, classes, and fees.</li>
    <li>To send relevant updates via WhatsApp for reminders, class changes, and notifications.</li>
    <li>To track admin operations like role assignment and fee management.</li>
</ul>

<h4>3. Data Security</h4>
<p>All user passwords are encrypted and stored securely. We use role-based access control to ensure that only authorized personnel can access or modify data.</p>

<h4>4. WhatsApp Communication</h4>
<p>We use WhatsApp Cloud API to send official messages such as fee reminders, class cancellations, and announcements. No promotional or third-party messages are sent.</p>

<h4>5. Data Sharing</h4>
<p>We do not sell or share your data with any external parties, except when legally required or for technical infrastructure (e.g., WhatsApp API usage).</p>

<h4>6. Your Consent</h4>
<p>By using our platform and services, you consent to the terms of this privacy policy.</p>

<h4>7. Changes to this Policy</h4>
<p>We may update this policy periodically. All changes will be posted on this page with a revised "last updated" date.</p>

<h4>8. Contact Us</h4>
<p>If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy policy, please contact the school administration directly.</p>
